## COMPONENT DIRECTORY STRUCTURE

```
SYNAPSE/
├── src/              [Apache 2.0] - Compiler core
├── include/          [Apache 2.0] - Language definitions
├── stdlib/core.syn   [Apache 2.0] - Standard library
├── stdlib/io.syn     [Apache 2.0] - I/O operations
├── stdlib/crypto.syn [Apache 2.0] - Cryptographic primitives
│
├── stdlib/net/synapsefs.syn  [AGPL v3] - Blockchain filesystem
├── stdlib/net/p2p.syn        [AGPL v3] - P2P protocol
└── stdlib/swarm/hive.syn     [AGPL v3] - Swarm intelligence

```

