By contributing to this project, you agree to license your contributions 
under the same terms as the component you're modifying:
- Contributions to Apache 2.0 components → Apache 2.0
- Contributions to AGPL v3 components → AGPL v3

All contributions must include the Contributor License Agreement (CLA).

